high_descs: Head left to reach the shelf.

Turn around and head left to exit the room and turn right to head to the living room on the right to reach the coffee table.
Put the tomato on the coffee table.

Pick up the tomato on the right from the desk.
Turn around and head left to exit the room and turn right to head to the living room on the right to reach the coffee table.
Put the tomato on the coffee table with the other tomato.
